HEADWORD: Pard
<hw>Pard</hw> <pr>(p⟦aum⟧rd)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pardus</ets>, Gr. <grk>pa`rdos</grk>; cf. Skr.
<ets>p⟦rsdot⟧d⟦amac⟧ku</ets> tiger, panther.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
